<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>GA4 → CEP Event &amp; Parameter Mapping</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont@latest/tabler-icons.min.css">
<style>

:root{--bg:#fff;--bg-2:#f5f4f0;--bg-info:#E6F1FB;--txt:#1a1a18;--txt-2:#73726c;--txt-3:#888780;--txt-info:#185FA5;--bdr:rgba(0,0,0,.10);--bdr-2:rgba(0,0,0,.18);--bdr-info:#378ADD;--r:8px;--rl:12px}
@media(prefers-color-scheme:dark){:root{--bg:#1c1c1a;--bg-2:#252523;--bg-info:#042C53;--txt:#e8e7e0;--txt-2:#888780;--txt-3:#73726c;--txt-info:#85B7EB;--bdr:rgba(255,255,255,.10);--bdr-2:rgba(255,255,255,.18)}}
*,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
body{font-family:-apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,'Segoe UI',Roboto,'Helvetica Neue',Arial,sans-serif;background:var(--bg);color:var(--txt);line-height:1.5;padding:2rem 1.5rem;max-width:1060px;margin:0 auto}
.hdr{margin-bottom:1.75rem;padding-bottom:1.25rem;border-bottom:.5px solid var(--bdr-2)}
.hdr h1{font-size:22px;font-weight:500;margin-bottom:6px}.hdr p{font-size:14px;color:var(--txt-2)}
.sg{display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,minmax(0,1fr));gap:10px;margin:0 0 1.25rem}
.sc{background:var(--bg-2);border-radius:var(--r);padding:12px 16px}
.sn{font-size:24px;font-weight:500;line-height:1.1;margin-bottom:2px}.sl{font-size:12px;color:var(--txt-2)}
.info{border:.5px solid var(--bdr-info);border-radius:var(--r);padding:10px 14px;margin-bottom:1rem;font-size:12px;color:var(--txt-info);background:var(--bg-info);line-height:1.6}
.legend{display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:.8rem;font-size:12px;color:var(--txt-2);align-items:center}
.filters{display:flex;gap:8px;flex-wrap:wrap;margin-bottom:1rem}
.fb{padding:5px 14px;border-radius:20px;border:.5px solid var(--bdr-2);background:transparent;color:var(--txt-2);cursor:pointer;font-size:12px;font-family:inherit;transition:background .12s,color .12s}
.fb:hover{background:var(--bg-2)}.fb.on{background:var(--txt);color:var(--bg);border-color:transparent}
.tbl-wrap{border:.5px solid var(--bdr);border-radius:var(--rl);overflow:hidden}.tbl-scroll{overflow-x:auto}
table{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;min-width:640px}
th{padding:8px 12px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:var(--txt-2);letter-spacing:.04em;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:.5px solid var(--bdr-2);text-align:left;white-space:nowrap;background:var(--bg-2)}
.mr td{padding:9px 12px;font-size:13px;border-bottom:.5px solid var(--bdr);vertical-align:middle;cursor:pointer}
.mr:hover td{background:var(--bg-2)}.mr.open td{border-bottom:none;background:var(--bg-2)}
.dr{display:none}.dr.show{display:table-row}
.dr>td{padding:0;border-bottom:.5px solid var(--bdr)}
.di{padding:0;background:var(--bg);border-top:2px solid var(--bdr-info)}
.det-grid{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:0}
@media(max-width:720px){.det-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
.det-col{padding:14px 16px}
.det-col+.det-col{border-left:.5px solid var(--bdr)}
@media(max-width:720px){.det-col+.det-col{border-left:none;border-top:.5px solid var(--bdr)}}
.col-hd{font-size:11px;font-weight:600;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.06em;color:var(--txt-2);margin-bottom:10px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.sec-sub{font-size:11px;font-weight:500;color:var(--txt-2);text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.04em;margin:10px 0 5px;padding-bottom:3px;border-bottom:.5px solid var(--bdr)}
.sec-sub:first-of-type{margin-top:0}
.cep-chips{display:flex;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:3px;margin-top:2px}
.cp{display:inline-block;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:10px;font-family:'Menlo','Consolas','Monaco',monospace;font-size:11px;background:var(--bg-2);border:.5px solid var(--bdr-2);color:var(--txt-2)}
.cp-r{background:#EAF3DE;border-color:transparent;color:#27500A;font-weight:600}
.cp sup{font-size:8px;vertical-align:super}
@media(prefers-color-scheme:dark){.cp-r{background:#173404;color:#C0DD97}}
.ev-lbl{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;padding:3px 10px 3px 8px;background:var(--bg-2);border-radius:var(--r);border-left:3px solid var(--bdr-info);margin:10px 0 6px}
.ev-lbl:first-of-type{margin-top:0}
.pt{width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;font-size:12px}
.pt td{padding:3px 6px;border-bottom:.5px solid var(--bdr);vertical-align:top}
.pt tr:last-child td{border-bottom:none}
.pt td:first-child{font-weight:500;color:var(--txt);white-space:nowrap;font-family:'Menlo','Consolas','Monaco',monospace;font-size:11px;width:44%}
.pt td:nth-child(2){color:var(--txt-3);font-family:'Menlo','Consolas','Monaco',monospace;font-size:11px;word-break:break-all}
.sc-e{display:inline-block;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;background:#E6F1FB;color:#0C447C}
.sc-i{display:inline-block;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;background:#EAF3DE;color:#27500A}
.sc-u{display:inline-block;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;background:#EEEDFE;color:#3C3489}
.sc-bq{display:inline-block;padding:1px 5px;border-radius:3px;font-size:10px;font-weight:500;background:#FAEEDA;color:#633806}
@media(prefers-color-scheme:dark){.sc-e{background:#042C53;color:#B5D4F4}.sc-i{background:#173404;color:#C0DD97}.sc-u{background:#26215C;color:#CECBF6}.sc-bq{background:#412402;color:#FAC775}}
.glb-note{font-size:11px;color:var(--txt-3);margin-top:5px}
.none-note{font-size:12px;color:var(--txt-3);font-style:italic;padding:4px 0}
.tbtn{width:20px;height:20px;border-radius:3px;border:.5px solid var(--bdr-2);background:transparent;cursor:pointer;color:var(--txt-2);font-size:9px;display:inline-flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;font-family:inherit;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:6px;padding:0}
.tbtn .ti{transition:transform .2s;display:block}.tbtn.open .ti{transform:rotate(90deg)}
.bdg{display:inline-block;padding:2px 7px;border-radius:4px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;white-space:nowrap;line-height:1.6}
.pll{display:inline-block;padding:1px 7px;border-radius:10px;font-size:11px;font-weight:500;margin:1px 2px 1px 0;white-space:nowrap}
.nt{font-size:11px;color:var(--txt-3);margin-top:4px;line-height:1.4}
/* Original framework colors */
.fw-pf{background:#EEEDFE;color:#3C3489}.fw-pi{background:#E1F5EE;color:#085041}.fw-po{background:#E6F1FB;color:#0C447C}.fw-na{background:#EAF3DE;color:#27500A}.fw-me{background:#FAEEDA;color:#633806}.fw-pp{background:#FAECE7;color:#712B13}.fw-fa{background:#FBEAF0;color:#72243E}.fw-ex{background:#F1EFE8;color:#444441}.fw-fb{background:#E6F1FB;color:#0C447C}.fw-fd{background:#E1F5EE;color:#085041}.fw-si{background:#FAECE7;color:#712B13}
/* New framework colors */
.fw-rr{background:#FEF3E2;color:#6B3A00}.fw-ss{background:#E2F7F0;color:#00574B}.fw-ci{background:#EDE9FE;color:#4C1D95}
/* Type colors */
.c-std{background:#EAF3DE;color:#27500A}.c-multi{background:#EEEDFE;color:#3C3489}.c-cond{background:#FAEEDA;color:#633806}.c-none{background:#F1EFE8;color:#5F5E5A}
.foot{font-size:11px;color:var(--txt-2);margin-top:.85rem;line-height:1.6}
@media(prefers-color-scheme:dark){
  .fw-pf{background:#26215C;color:#CECBF6}.fw-pi{background:#04342C;color:#9FE1CB}.fw-po{background:#042C53;color:#B5D4F4}.fw-na{background:#173404;color:#C0DD97}.fw-me{background:#412402;color:#FAC775}.fw-pp{background:#4A1B0C;color:#F5C4B3}.fw-fa{background:#4B1528;color:#F4C0D1}.fw-ex{background:#2C2C2A;color:#B4B2A9}.fw-fb{background:#042C53;color:#B5D4F4}.fw-fd{background:#04342C;color:#9FE1CB}.fw-si{background:#4A1B0C;color:#F5C4B3}
  .fw-rr{background:#3D2000;color:#FBBF24}.fw-ss{background:#002820;color:#6EE7B7}.fw-ci{background:#2E1065;color:#C4B5FD}
  .c-std{background:#173404;color:#C0DD97}.c-multi{background:#26215C;color:#CECBF6}.c-cond{background:#412402;color:#FAC775}.c-none{background:#2C2C2A;color:#B4B2A9}
  #sn-ga4{color:#C0DD97!important}#sn-none{color:#B4B2A9!important}#sn-multi{color:#CECBF6!important}
}
@media print{.filters,.tbtn{display:none}.dr{display:none!important}body{padding:1rem;max-width:100%}}

/* ── Filter tooltips ── */
.fb[data-tip]{position:relative}
.fb[data-tip]::after{
  content:attr(data-tip);
  position:absolute;top:calc(100% + 8px);left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
  background:var(--txt);color:var(--bg);
  padding:6px 11px;border-radius:6px;
  font-size:11px;font-weight:400;line-height:1.5;
  white-space:normal;text-align:center;max-width:220px;
  pointer-events:none;opacity:0;transition:opacity .15s;z-index:200;
}
.fb[data-tip]::before{
  content:'';position:absolute;top:calc(100% + 2px);left:50%;transform:translateX(-50%);
  border:5px solid transparent;border-bottom-color:var(--txt);
  pointer-events:none;opacity:0;transition:opacity .15s;z-index:200;
}
.fb[data-tip]:hover::after,.fb[data-tip]:hover::before{opacity:1}
.filters{position:relative;z-index:10}


/* ── GA4→CEP additions ── */
.cat-custom{background:#E6F1FB;color:#0C447C}
.cat-ecomm{background:#FAEEDA;color:#633806}
@media(prefers-color-scheme:dark){.cat-custom{background:#042C53;color:#B5D4F4}.cat-ecomm{background:#412402;color:#FAC775}}
.tagname{font-weight:500;font-size:13px;line-height:1.3}
.ev-code{display:inline-block;font-family:'Menlo','Consolas','Monaco',monospace;font-size:11px;color:var(--txt-2);background:var(--bg-2);padding:1px 6px;border-radius:4px;margin-top:4px}
.tagref{font-size:11px;color:var(--txt-3);font-family:'Menlo','Consolas','Monaco',monospace;margin:-2px 0 9px;word-break:break-word}
.fire-note{font-size:12px;color:var(--txt-2);margin-top:8px;line-height:1.55;padding:8px 11px;background:var(--bg-2);border-radius:6px}
.fire-note strong{color:var(--txt);font-weight:600}
.cep-block + .cep-block{margin-top:15px;padding-top:14px;border-top:.5px dashed var(--bdr-2)}
/* event-type dropdown */
.dd{position:relative;display:inline-block}
.dd-btn{display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:6px}
.dd-btn .ti{font-size:13px;transition:transform .2s}
.dd-btn.open .ti{transform:rotate(180deg)}
.dd-panel{position:absolute;top:calc(100% + 6px);left:0;z-index:50;background:var(--bg);border:.5px solid var(--bdr-2);border-radius:var(--r);padding:6px;min-width:210px;box-shadow:0 6px 24px rgba(0,0,0,.14);display:none}
.dd-panel.open{display:block}
.dd-opt{display:flex;align-items:center;gap:9px;padding:7px 9px;border-radius:6px;font-size:12px;color:var(--txt);cursor:pointer;user-select:none}
.dd-opt:hover{background:var(--bg-2)}
.dd-opt input{appearance:none;-webkit-appearance:none;width:15px;height:15px;border:1.5px solid var(--bdr-2);border-radius:4px;cursor:pointer;position:relative;margin:0;flex:none}
.dd-opt input:checked{background:var(--txt);border-color:var(--txt)}
.dd-opt input:checked::after{content:'';position:absolute;left:4px;top:1px;width:4px;height:8px;border:solid var(--bg);border-width:0 2px 2px 0;transform:rotate(45deg)}
.dd-opt .cnt{color:var(--txt-3);font-size:11px;margin-left:auto}
.filt-lbl{font-size:12px;color:var(--txt-2);align-self:center}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<div class="hdr">
  <h1>GA4 &rarr; CEP Event &amp; Parameter Mapping</h1>
  <p>Unique 69 GA4 events across 81 GTM tags &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Click any row to see GA4 parameters + the mapped CEP Key properties &nbsp;&middot;&nbsp; Updated 12th June 2026</p>
</div>

<div class="sg">
  <div class="sc"><div class="sn" id="sn-total">81</div><div class="sl">GA4 event tags</div></div>
  <div class="sc"><div class="sn" style="color:#3B6D11" id="sn-map">30</div><div class="sl">Map to CEP</div></div>
  <div class="sc"><div class="sn" style="color:#5F5E5A" id="sn-no">51</div><div class="sl">No CEP event</div></div>
  <div class="sc"><div class="sn" style="color:#3C3489" id="sn-mul">9</div><div class="sl">Multi-event routing</div></div>
</div>

<div class="info">
  <strong>15 global params pass with every GA4 event (not repeated in expanded rows):</strong>
  page_name &middot; page_type &middot; gtm_id &middot; gtm_language &middot; user_id &middot; traffic_type &middot; store_type &middot; gtm_country &middot; gtm_currency &middot; ftb &middot; onetrust_consent &middot; login &middot; gtm_internal_user_uscd (user) &middot; gtm_user_id (user) &middot; gtm_anonymous_user_id (user)
</div>

<div class="legend">
  <strong>Mapping key:</strong>
  <span><span class="pll c-std">Mapped</span> 1 CEP event</span>
  <span><span class="pll c-multi">Multi-map</span> &gt;1 CEP event</span>
  <span><span class="pll c-none">No CEP</span> GA4 only</span>
  &nbsp;
  <span style="font-size:11px"><span class="cp cp-r" style="padding:1px 6px;font-size:10px">prop<sup>*</sup></span> = required / highly recommended</span>
</div>

<div class="filters">
  <button class="fb pill on" data-tip="All GA4 event tags" onclick="setPill('all',this)">All (<span id="c-all">88</span>)</button>
  <button class="fb pill" data-tip="Events currently tracked in GA4 that will also be tracked in CEP" onclick="setPill('hascep',this)">Has CEP (<span id="c-has">30</span>)</button>
  <button class="fb pill" data-tip="Events tracked in GA4 only" onclick="setPill('nocep',this)">No CEP (<span id="c-no">58</span>)</button>
  <button class="fb pill" data-tip="GA4 events mapped to multiple CEP events" onclick="setPill('multi',this)">Multi-event (<span id="c-mul">9</span>)</button>
  <div class="dd">
    <button class="fb dd-btn" id="dd-btn" onclick="toggleDD(event)">Event type: <span id="dd-state">All types</span> <i class="ti ti-chevron-down"></i></button>
    <div class="dd-panel" id="dd-panel">
      <label class="dd-opt"><input type="checkbox" id="f-custom" checked onchange="go()"> Custom Events <span class="cnt">(77)</span></label>
      <label class="dd-opt"><input type="checkbox" id="f-ecomm" checked onchange="go()"> Ecommerce Event <span class="cnt">(11)</span></label>
    </div>
  </div>
  <span class="filt-lbl" style="margin-left:auto">Showing <strong id="shown-count">88</strong></span>
</div>

<div class="tbl-wrap"><div class="tbl-scroll">
  <table>
    <thead><tr>
      <th style="width:16%">Event type</th>
      <th style="width:34%">GA4 event (GTM tag)</th>
      <th style="width:36%">CEP event(s)</th>
      <th style="width:14%">Mapping</th>
    </tr></thead>
    <tbody id="tbl"></tbody>
  </table>
</div></div>

<p class="foot">Source: <em>Implementation Squad &mdash; GA4_to_CEP_Event_Mapping</em>. Parameters are grouped by scope (event / item / user). CEP properties marked <strong>*</strong> are required or highly recommended. Events that map to more than one CEP event list each CEP event with its own parameters and firing conditions.</p>

